name: 12 Memory Card - Otta
description: This otter loves the view of the sea and enjoys a can of sardines in lemon sauce. When he faced storms and big waves, he did not dampen his courage and was even challenged to conquer them. A sailor who is respected by his sailing crew. His grandfather is known as a legend who is nicknamed the Conqueror Behemoth (A fish who rules the world)! whoa, amazing, isn't it?!
